STRICT USAGE RESTRICTIONS:

1. PROHIBITED USES - This Software must NOT be used for:
   a) Scraping Jiji.ug or any website without explicit written permission
   b) Harvesting personal data (phone numbers, emails, addresses)
   c) Violating any website's Terms of Service or robots.txt
   d) Commercial data collection or resale
   e) Unsolicited marketing, spam, or harassment
   f) Any activity that violates data protection laws
   g) Competitive intelligence without authorization
   h) Fraud, identity theft, or other criminal activities
   i) Any purpose that infringes on individual privacy rights
   j) Overwhelming servers or denial of service activities

2. PERMITTED USES - This Software MAY ONLY be used for:
   a) Studying web scraping techniques and browser automation
   b) Learning Python, Playwright, and data extraction concepts
   c) Portfolio or resume demonstration (code only, not execution)
   d) Educational coursework or research with proper supervision
   e) Scraping your own websites or test environments
   f) Scraping websites where you have explicit written permission
   g) Practicing on designated scraping sandboxes (e.g., toscrape.com)

